@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sqipza(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((tmp * wp.sin(v1 + 0.19)) - v2)
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.22 + tmp + 0.21) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.39)))
    tmp = wp.abs(((v2 + 1.00 / v0 + 0.30) - v1))
    data[tid] = v0
